    <h2 class="wow fadeIn">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.5s">There are many ways to be more green and to preserve our world. <br>
    If we want to have a cleaner world and a more sustainable lifestyle we have to invest in clean and <b>renewable energy.</b> <br>
    With our app we wish to <b>promote solar energy,</b> which is free and does not compromise the environment, our health and climate. <br>
    Nevertheless, solar energy is inexhaustible. <br>
    For all these reasons solar energy should become the primary form of energy:
    this could bring to a <b>cleaner</b> environment and a healthier world. <br>
    Solar energy is the key to allow technology and nature to co-exist peacefully. <br>
    We guess that solar energy will be affordable and <b>available everywhere</b> in the world for generations to come.</p>

        <div class="linkBox wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
